Business Brief -- Finmeccanica S.p.A.:
   Capital Increase Stepped Up
   In Proposal to Go Public
The Finmeccanica group includes a railroad equipment
maker, an aerospace and defense unit, and an automation
controls subsidiary. It also holds interests in energy
generation, bioengineering and microprocessors. Eventually as
much as 40% of Finmeccanica's share capital is expected to be
traded.
   Sources familiar with the restructuring said it probably
will happen in the fall.